messageBody:
I thought I knew, but just this weekend at a Wendy's fast food
restaurant in Maine, I saw "JUnit '05" scribbled on the door to a
bathroom stall. I tried to find out more about this JUnit vandal, but
all Google will give me is very helpful documentation about a unit
testing framework for Java. Frustrating, that.

David Saff
